Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down a difficult road\Nfilled with endless struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you are going\Nfollowing someone else's map?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An insightful crow comes along\Nto tear up the map
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now open your eyes and\Ntake a look at the truth (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to lose,\Nso let's GO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh!\NJust go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's go,"\Nwith so much energy…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You’re in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because! Because!\Nlt's in the middle of my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three steps\Nin the training, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m only done with the second step!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do the third step\Neven while walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this…?\NAn ordinary balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first step is “Spin.”\NThe second step is “Power.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, the third step is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Impossible Choice:\NThe Pain Within Tsunade's Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is “this”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me, it looks as if\NI am simply holding a balloon…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it “looks as if,”\Nbut nothing is really happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will do the same thing\Non my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see what’s really happening\Ninside the balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chakra is randomly spinning\Nand going faster and faster…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, it’s perfectly round…\Nlt’s almost like…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a small typhoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s happening in your left hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is happening inside that balloon\Nin your right hand, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The balloon isn’t moving at all\Neven if he’s spinning that much Chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s more power than\Nthat time the rubber ball popped,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it’s spinning a lot more too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, in this third step,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’ve got to use 100% of\Nwhat you have learned…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and retain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, while keeping\Nthe “Spin” and the “Power” at their max,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,imagine creating a single layer\Nwithin the balloon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and compressing the Chakra within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this training is about keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the spin and power that I did\Nin the second step,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and conversely,\Ntrying not to pop a delicate balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That’s the most perceptive\Nyou've been so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what’s the point in going\Nto all the trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it means this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch! It’s like this up until\Nthe second step of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, after you have mastered\Nthe third step!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can keep this small typhoon\Nthe size of your palm,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the force won’t disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spinning gets faster and faster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the power gets\Nmore and more compressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the destructive power\Nwill reach its max.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so, that’s that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I’ll do this, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this feels right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retain it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retain…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retain…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No cutting-corners!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got to put out 100% spin and power,\Nand retain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I can perfectly control all my power,\Nit’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can see it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This third step…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s on a totally different level\Ncompared to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With an achievement difficulty of Rank A,\Nit’s a super advanced Ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I’m done explaining!\NWe’ll continue as we go on walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t need to rush so much,\Nuntil I can properly…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have already wasted enough time\Nwaiting for your body to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no guarantee that\NTsunade stays in this town much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like an old acquaintance\Nis going to conveniently pop up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and start talking about\Nthe good old times with her…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see…Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d looked for you everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me\Nafter so long a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren’t thinking of talking\Nabout the old days…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I need to ask you\Nfor a little favor…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heartbeat is fast…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that complexion,\Nhe must have a high fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been fatigued\Nfor quite some time…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that arm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have understood by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to someone else,\NI don’t treat anyone any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won’t do…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know how serious\Nthis wound is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can treat this wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one of the Legendary “Sannin”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who won her fame as\Na medical specialist, Princess Tsunade…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That arm…\Nit’s not an ordinary wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special Sealing Jutsu or something…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it just happened…\Nwhen I killed the Third Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You… Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. Don’t look so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything that has a form\Nwill one day decay…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must already know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you have let two of\Nyour most beloved ones die…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let two of the most beloved ones die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see… He thinks of terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a really terrible way to die…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poisoned…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won’t let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Shizune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This attendant…is an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality's been like this\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know my personality\Nvery well…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stop fooling around with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll kill you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s powerful…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so scary…\Nshe definitely must be single.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunade is impatient and short-tempered…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Naruto,\Nthere’s no time to be falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don’t hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows where that shrew\Nwill disappear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, Pervy Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s no way to speak to\Na hard-working apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Tsunade is the first priority now,\Nnot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what the heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To have this Pervy Sage come\Nall the way to meet her…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could this Kunoichi Tsunade be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope she’s still here…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn’t come here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just want to negotiate with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve already told you once.\NGet out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one\Nwho can treat Lord Orochimaru’s arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re not asking you to do it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s make a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll count up to five.\NLeave before I’m done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, I’ll make you disappear myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.\Nlt won’t be a bad deal for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll resurrect the little brother\Nand man, both of whom you loved…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Forbidden Jutsu I’ve developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we haven’t disappeared yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m guessing that the deal is made?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I do know this young lady…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To win back the money she lost here,\NI think she said…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was going over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin… Power…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting them out to their max\Nand retain it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna gamble a bit, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there? Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, if the total number of the pips\Non these dices
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comes out as even numbers,\Nthat’s “Cho”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if it’s odd, that’s “Han.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I am training right now,\Ndon’t bug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense!\NThis is a gambling house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of that balloon,\Nlet’s play with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:17:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I don’t have any time\Nto be playing with those dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, what a boring kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…can you tell me where that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can’t expect things to be free\Nin a gambling house, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s make a deal.\NThe information will be free if you win…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you lose,\NI’ll give it to you for 1000 ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So choose, odd or even!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Here we go…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so…\Nsince I am exactly 50 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go for…even!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s odd, I win…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll open it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! 2 and 5, odd!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 ryo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I won…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! It didn’t work again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retain…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where shall I look next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she’s nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lotto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, grownups, everyone loves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and play with\Nthis fun, fun Lotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s one that you know\Nthe result right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you are so much cuter\Nbeing chubby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe he won\Nwith just one draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s very talented in this…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though his talent in Jutsu\Nis still immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…anyhow…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could have Tsunade gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn’t have gone that far\Nin this short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we’ll have to\Nsearch for her from a higher place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember it correctly,\Nthis is a castle town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go up to the castle…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you want to see those two…\NTsunade?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nawaki…Dan…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I treat your arms,\Nwhat do you intend to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don’t like to lie…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I will tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Where is the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not there…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to getting what I want…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I will completely destroy\Nthe Leaf Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cycle of hardship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside, we were crying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one thing we won't give up\Nis the dream we've chosen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secondary role,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a role in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reaching for that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us stay centered,\Nlet us stay true
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe hung on without giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe kept coming back up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe believed and dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe've seen fools
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if she is one of the Sannin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if she is\Nthe legendary Kunoichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if she's\Nthe medical specialist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll accept\Nthis person as the new Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she belittles the Third\Nand Fourth Hokages…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if she's the candidate\Nto be the Fifth Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick her butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:\N "Unforgivable! A Total Lack of Respect!"
